<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>WhatsApp Release Notes - {{version}}</title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 20px auto;
  max-width: 800px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
h1 { color: #075E54; }
h2 { color: #128C7E; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>WhatsApp Release Notes</h1>

<p><strong>Release Version:</strong> {{version}}<br>
<strong>Release Date:</strong> {{date}}<br>
<strong>Release Type:</strong> {{type}}<br>
<strong>Product:</strong> {{product}}<br>
<strong>Author:</strong> {{author}}<br>
<strong>Audience:</strong> {{audience}}</p>

<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>{{summary}}</p>

<h2>New Features</h2>
<ul>
{{#each new_features}}
<li>{{this}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Improvements</h2>
<ul>
{{#each improvements}}
<li>{{this}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
{{#each bug_fixes}}
<li>{{this}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Breaking Changes</h2>
<p>{{breaking_changes}}</p>

<h2>Known Issues</h2>
<p>{{known_issues}}</p>

<h2>Related Information</h2>
<p>For help and feature tips, visit <a href="https://www.whatsapp.com/help">WhatsApp Help Center</a>.<br>
To report issues, go to <strong>Settings > Help > Contact Us</strong> within the app.</p>

</body>
</html>
